name: Hawkes Transitional Residence
review_text: THIS is the PERFECT living facility to help a homeless person to transition back into permanent housing. Here, it is a TEAM effort... if you do YOUR part, they will do THEIRS to help you in ANY way that they can, just as they have done for ME. I have a BEAUTIFUL private room with a view; It's not at ALL what one's impression of a "shelter" would be like... it resembles more of a hotel... fabulous!!
